ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"不分化"},{"pid":"cdee2fe84c3b73374347169d146d2accb305b348","tid":1457841,"uid":115836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:51:35.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n鬼到仆街<br />\n連登都好多post又屌人走又話後悔叫人走，明明今次係策略成功<br />\n今日就算犧牲幾多個人對對家影響都唔會差好遠，但係對我們影響好大呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d3feeea8f0d912fd4fd2ee827c4cc55b808d29","tid":1457841,"uid":160348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4938c13a5095a1d8d1522ff2bee98558001a1d48","tid":1457841,"uid":7270,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:33:12.000Z","msg":"商界最怕一樣嘢，就係估你唔到（uncertainty）。任何一樣嘢長期發生就必定估到（certainty)，商界就會有對策。因此，連續N日令機場癱瘓、連續佔領道路等行動對商界個影響冇突發性癱瘓機場咁金。如果N日冇機場，商界可以安排車隊，如果N日塞路，商界可以改路。但如果有機場但又唔知幾時要關閉，咁就效應大。效應要大必要估你唔到。<br />\n<br />\nWater嘅形態正正係估佢唔到。<br />\n<br />\nBe water。<br />\n<br />\n經濟手段好撚有用，一定要繼續！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"Yes this is the essence <br />\nNo point to stay but we have to make random attacks"},{"pid":"29822eca1ba0d6b91038a8366ef3fe7eaeee0435","tid":1457841,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"至少定性左同西藏同埋新疆一樣既程度 黨國機器開始黎料"},{"pid":"96275f88618e6cb59601867171ab0d6a02764807","tid":1457841,"uid":294068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:52:07.000Z","msg":"照咁講人少先更加會鎮壓lo, 人山人海咁你想點搞？1打100？"},{"pid":"b6d2b3a24f6d43d8967c817a2c5d06b37afd484c","tid":1457841,"uid":412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:52:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Be WATER 不分化</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3f84e9593b50ffec058f7ccd30caa4eca7db7c96","tid":1457841,"uid":207858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"