25b5258","tid":1457841,"uid":264626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:04:29.000Z","msg":"中共開始心急，想九月前平息事件迎國慶。<br />\n<br />\n八月好重要，唔可以好似呢幾日咁不斷送頭，唔係九月前捉哂前線就收皮。<br />\n<br />\n係咪可以暫時以和理非為主，勇武為副？"},{"pid":"631985d54e60aa6c53fd7accafb6795f50823e5c","tid":1457841,"uid":254645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bc4f2753aa75c5fbe1ed6d3e1cc5fe8e7e47f26","tid":1457841,"uid":280436,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:25:48.000Z","msg":"政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">操縱緊我地嘅言論</span></span>去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">分化</span></span>勇武同和理非<br />\n<br />\n大量網軍混入連登，Facebook，telegram<br />\n散播謠言<br />\n令大家<span style=\"color: red;\">質疑</span>盟友嘅可信性<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">互相猜忌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果散</span> <br />\n就發表大量<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌撚散水狗</span></span></span>嘅言論<br />\n馬後砲<br />\n指責班合理擔心安全嘅和理非<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">be water</span></span>係大家一直以來重視嘅嘢<br />\n根本勇武唔會怪責<br />\n可見係政府故意引起割席<br />\n<br />\n如果<span style=\"color: red;\">唔散</span><br />\n警察真係做嘢<br />\n就會湧現和理非怪責勇武嘅言論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一切 都係政府設下嘅套路！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日真係有取消/延誤航班 <br />\n警察真係有佈防 而且有機會用得到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但真正目的並非實質行動<br />\n而係分化大家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最近安插臥底係前線同樣<br />\n都有一層目的係為左令尼場運動嘅參與者<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自行瓦解</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家千奇唔好中佢嘅計</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">謹記 不分化 不割席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢嘅陰濕招數 我地只要團結 一定搵到方法破解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:06:44.000Z","msg":"agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0d7ece7576c779d04d6d93a1d05ef7229e607a","tid":1457841,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"我都懷疑緊，警方見示威者散左大部份，計劃穿煲，於是至改變計劃，唔行動住。<br />\n(所以若果頭先大部份唔走，反而會見到警方清場)<br />\n(純猜測)"},{"pid":"5b5f4c941ee72a0404a45180d648d102fdc96983","tid":1457841,"uid":255816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:15:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89fa7fef94338c2e802a76e029fb1912acbecb0d","tid":1457841,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"219b133208c9506fbe4e5e5554bcf783d373fc57","tid":1457841,"uid":125469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29ea1ec807c543893613e7d8d21dae63daa223fe","tid":1457841,"uid":114179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:23:07.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"你開左我唔洗開po啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBetween 補充下<br />\n<br />\n如果今日冇散，可能真係入黎拉人清場<br />\n散左咁黑驚就達到佢既目的<br />\n<br />\n所以下次再係咁建議散去東涌先，冇事就入番去，彈出彈入"},{"pid":"4919de65fc6b5b765aa931d7b7d0c07165b9c1fb","tid":1457841,"uid":283972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13da86a374d0c3e60c1b0a6b79078464d2ae00a","tid":1457841,"uid":60583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:24:22.000Z","msg":"同意推post"},{"pid":"3ff200ae6